trans-unit.source: Indicates the first week of the year to use when calling date-related functions.
trans-unit.target: 指示呼叫日期相關函式時所要使用年份的第一週。

trans-unit.source: When you call date-related functions, you can use the following enumeration members in your code in place of the actual values.
trans-unit.target: 當您呼叫日期相關函式時，您可以使用下列的列舉型別成員在您的程式碼，用來取代實際的值。

trans-unit.source: Some date-related functions take a `DayOfWeek` argument, a `WeekOfYear` argument, or both.
trans-unit.target: 某些日期相關函式接受`DayOfWeek`引數，`WeekOfYear`引數，或兩者。

trans-unit.source: The `FirstWeekOfYear` enumeration specifies the valid values for the `WeekOfYear` arguments, as well as the possible return values from the functions.
trans-unit.target: `FirstWeekOfYear`列舉值會指定有效的值`WeekOfYear`引數，以及可能的傳回值的函式。

trans-unit.source: The `WeekOfYear` argument takes the `FirstWeekOfYear` enumeration members.
The first week that has at least four days in the new year.
trans-unit.target: 至少有四個天新年度的第一週。

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFourDays" name="vbFirstFourDays" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是相當於 Visual Basic 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFourDays" name="vbFirstFourDays" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The first full week of the year.
trans-unit.target: 年中的第一個完整的星期。

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFullWeek" name="vbFirstFullWeek" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是相當於 Visual Basic 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstFullWeek" name="vbFirstFullWeek" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The week in which January 1 occurs (default).
trans-unit.target: 一週發生在哪個年 1 月 1 （預設值）。

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstJan1" name="vbFirstJan1" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是相當於 Visual Basic 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbFirstJan1" name="vbFirstJan1" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The weekspecified in your system settings as the first week of the year.
trans-unit.target: 在 系統設定為一年的第一週 weekspecified。

trans-unit.source: This member is equivalent to the Visual Basic constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbUseSystem" name="vbUseSystem" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是相當於 Visual Basic 常數<xref uid="langword_csharp_vbUseSystem" name="vbUseSystem" href=""> </xref>。
